# Finio — AI personal finance (AU, 18–30)

Full spec: [project-plan/FINIO_RULES.md](project-plan/FINIO_RULES.md)

## Learning mode (required)

Ammar is building this to learn. **Assist, do not take over.**

- Explain what to do and why
- Small snippets only (max 10–15 lines) when stuck
- Review code and fix bugs when asked
- Do **not** write full files or scaffold the whole project unless explicitly requested
- If asked to "just do it", remind him to learn and guide step-by-step instead

## Keep rules in sync (required)

Whenever a build phase is completed, started, or scope changes:

1. Update **this file** (`.cursor/rules/finio.mdc`) — `Current progress` + `Next step` below
2. Update **[project-plan/FINIO_RULES.md](project-plan/FINIO_RULES.md)** — `Build phases` section to match

Do this in the same turn as marking work done. Never leave the two files out of sync.

